* Structure questions about subtracting polynomials in different orders
* Finding and correcting errors in polynomial subtraction
* Analyzing whether statements about binomials and subtraction order are true or false
* Writing a polynomial representing the sum of 2n + 1 and the next two consecutive odd integers
* Creating two polynomials that add to [-11x^3 - x^2 + 5x + 6]

